### Context Menu API

**USE**: `ContextMenu` from `@api/ContextMenu`

**Available functions:**
- `addContextMenuPatch(navId, patch)` - Patch specific context menu
- `addGlobalContextMenuPatch(patch)` - Patch all context menus
- `removeContextMenuPatch(navId, patch)` - Remove patch
- `removeGlobalContextMenuPatch(patch)` - Remove global patch
- `findGroupChildrenByChildId(id, children, matchSubstring?)` - Find menu group

**DO NOT**: Directly modify context menu React elements

```typescript
import { ContextMenu } from "@api";
import { Menu } from "@webpack/common";

ContextMenu.addContextMenuPatch("user-context", (children, props) => {
    const group = ContextMenu.findGroupChildrenByChildId("block", children);
    if (!group) return;
    
    group.push(
        <Menu.MenuItem
            id="my-action"
            label="My Action"
            action={() => console.log("Clicked!", props.user)}
        />
    );
});
```

