## UI Extension APIs

### Chat Buttons API

**USE**: `ChatButtons` from `@api/ChatButtons`

**Available functions:**
- `addChatBarButton(id, render, icon)` - Add button to chat input
- `removeChatBarButton(id)` - Remove button
- `ChatBarButton` component - Pre-built button component

**DO NOT**: Manually inject buttons into chat input

```typescript
import { ChatButtons } from "@api";
import { ChatBarButton } from "@api/ChatButtons";
import { MyIcon } from "./MyIcon";

ChatButtons.addChatBarButton("my-button", (props) => (
    <ChatBarButton
        tooltip="My Button"
        onClick={() => console.log("Clicked!")}
    >
        <MyIcon />
    </ChatBarButton>
), MyIcon);
```

---

### Header Bar API

**USE**: `HeaderBar` from `@api/HeaderBar`

**Available functions:**
- `addHeaderBarButton(id, render, priority?)` - Add button to header bar
- `removeHeaderBarButton(id)` - Remove button
- `addChannelToolbarButton(id, render, priority?)` - Add to channel toolbar
- `removeChannelToolbarButton(id)` - Remove from toolbar
- `HeaderBarButton` component - Header bar button component
- `ChannelToolbarButton` component - Toolbar button component

**DO NOT**: Manually patch header bar components

```typescript
import { HeaderBar } from "@api";
import { HeaderBarButton } from "@api/HeaderBar";
import { MyIcon } from "./MyIcon";

HeaderBar.addHeaderBarButton("my-header-button", () => (
    <HeaderBarButton
        icon={MyIcon}
        tooltip="My Button"
        onClick={() => console.log("Clicked!")}
    />
), 0);
```

