### User Setting Definitions API

**USE**: `UserSettingDefinitions` from `@api/UserSettingDefinitions`

**Available functions:**
- `getUserSettingDefinition<T>(group, name)` - Get setting definition
- `getUserSettingDefinitionLazy<T>(group, name)` - Lazy getter
- `UserSettingsDefinitions` - All definitions object

**DO NOT**: Directly access Discord's setting definitions

```typescript
import { UserSettingDefinitions } from "@api";

// Requires UserSettingDefinitionsAPI plugin as dependency
const definition = UserSettingDefinitions.getUserSettingDefinition("textAndImages", "renderSpoilers");
if (definition) {
    // Access definition metadata
    console.log(definition);
}
```

